<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA17">
<l>aṭiyum paṭikaṭappat tōṭicaimēṟ cella</l>
<l>muṭiyum vicumpaḷanta teṉpar – vaṭiyukirā</l>
<l>līrntā ṉiraṇiyaṉa tāka miruñciṟaippuḷ</l>
<l>ḷūrntā ṉulakaḷanta nāṉṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While [his] foot crossed the earth, while [his] arms went out to the directions,</l>
<l>his head measured the sky, they say, he who with shapely nails</l>
<l>clawed the chest of Hiraṇya, he who mounted on the large-winged bird,</l> 
<l>at the time he measured the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
